     <div style="width: 90%;  position: absolute; top: 20px; text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:200%;">106.1</p><p style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:20px;">Het installeren en configureren van X11</p></div>

<div style="position: absolute; top: 200px; left:400px; text-align:left; font-size:100%;">

<ul>
<li style="list-style:disc;">X</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">/etc/X11/xorg.conf</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">xwininfo</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">xdpyinfo</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">xhost</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">DISPLAY</li>
</ul>

</div>

	<div id="container" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; font-size:40%;">
